### Создать заказ
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "address": "ул. Ленина 1",
  "items": [
    {
      "itemId": 10,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Получить заказ
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

### Оплатить заказ картой (успех)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": "CARD"
}

### Оплатить заказ QR (отказ)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": "QR"
}

### Создать платёж напрямую (internal)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "paymentMethod": "CARD",
  "amount": 1500.00
}
